stival-in-Ahoy-eruit|access-date=27 April 2021|work=Rijnmond.nl|publisher=[[RTV_Rijnmond|RTV Rijnmond]]|language=NL|archive-date=2021-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211012135701/https://www.rijnmond.nl/nieuws/1199638/Zo-ziet-het-indrukwekkende-podium-voor-het-Eurovisie-Songfestival-in-Ahoy-eruit|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://esctoday.com/182842/eurovision-2021-the-stage-is-lit-and-in-full-action/|title=Eurovision 2021: The stage is lit and in full action!|last=Jiandani|first=Sanjay (Sergio)|date=22 April 2021|work=ESCToday|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426211816/http://esctoday.com/182842/eurovision-2021-the-stage-is-lit-and-in-full-action/|archive-date=26 April 2021|url-status=live|quote=For example, we have a TV screen that is 52 meters wide and 12 meters high. Inside there are doors that can open. That has never been done on such a scale.}}</ref> 舞台設計得到[[擴增實境|增強現實]]效果的補充。<ref>{{Cite web|date=28 April 2021|title=Augmented reality to play important role in 2021 contest|url=https://escxtra.com/2021/04/28/augmented-reality-to-play-important-role-in-2021-contest/|url-status=no|access-date=28 April 2021|work=ESCXTRA|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506121821/https://escxtra.com/2021/04/28/augmented-reality-to-play-important-role-in-2021-contest/}}</ref> 與2019年大賽不同的是，{{link-en|演員休息室|Green room|歌手休息室}}佈置在主表演場地，並包含了之前為站立觀眾保留的整個樓層空間，以方便[[保持社交距離|社交距離]]。<ref>{{Cite web|date=12 February 2021|title=Eurovision'21: Changes to Greenroom for the Contest|url=https://eurovoix.com/2021/02/12/eurovision21-changes-to-greenroom-for-the-contest/|access-date=22 March 2021|work=Eurovoix|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501155921/https://eurovoix.com/2021/02/12/eurovision21-changes-to-greenroom-for-the-contest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 參賽作品 ===
{{See also|{{link-en|欧洲歌唱大赛規則|Rules of the Eurovision Song Contest}}|}}
2020年6月18日，歐廣聯盟宣布，今年各代表團可以選擇使用預先錄製的和聲。每個代表團仍然可以選擇使用伴唱，無論是在舞台上還是台下，或者現場和錄製的伴唱組合。根據規則，所有演奏歌曲旋律的主唱必須仍然是現場演唱。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Granger|first=Anthony|date=18 June 2020|title=Pre-recorded Backing Vocals to Trialled at Eurovision For One Year|url=https://eurovoix.com/2020/06/18/pre-recorded-backing-vocals-to-trialled-at-eurovision-for-one-year|access-date=18 June 2020|work=Eurovoix|archive-date=23 June 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623055002/https://eurovoix.com/2020/06/18/pre-recorded-backing-vocals-to-trialled-at-eurovision-for-one-year/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=18 June 2020|title=Changes announced to ensure Eurovision comes|url=https://eurovision.tv/story/changes-announced-to-ensure-eurovision-comes-back-for-good|access-date=18 June 2020|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|archive-date=28 September 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928084631/https://eurovision.tv/story/changes-announced-to-ensure-eurovision-comes-back-for-good|url-status=live}}</ref>

2020年11月18日，歐廣聯盟透露，為了保證所有參賽者都能參加比賽，每個國家廣播公司都將在比賽前製作一個“現場直播”備份錄音，以供使用如果參與者無法前往鹿特丹，或在抵達時接受隔離。錄音是在錄音室環境中實時進行的（就像在比賽中一樣），錄音後沒有對人聲或表演本身的任何部分進行任何編輯。還透露了一套製作指南，以確保錄音的公平性和完整性。<ref>{{Cite web|date=18 November 2020|title=2021 artists to record song "live-on-tape" to ensure Contest will happen|url=https://eurovision.tv/story/2021-artists-to-record-song-live-on-tape-to-ensure-contest-will-happen|access-date=19 November 2020|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|archive-date=18 November 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118140312/https://eurovision.tv/story/2021-artists-to-record-song-live-on-tape-to-ensure-contest-will-happen|url-status=live}}</ref>

其他參賽規則在2021年的比賽中保持不變。這包括一首歌的最長長度為三分鐘，舞臺上最多可有六名表演者，以及作品（歌詞和音樂）不得在前一年的9月1日之前進行商業發行。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rules – Eurovision Song Contest|date=12 January 2017|url=https://eurovision.tv/about/rules|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506164157/https://eurovision.tv/about/rules/|archive-date=6 May 2021|access-date=4 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union}}</ref> 2020年比賽取消後，歐廣聯盟探索了允許2020年比賽中選擇的歌曲參加2021年比賽的選項，這需要與歐洲電視歌曲比賽參攷小組和國家廣播公司進行討論。<ref name="2020 cancellation" /> 2020年和2021年的保加利亞代表{{link-en|維多利亞·格奧爾基耶娃|Victoria Georgieva|維多利亞}}公開表示支持這一舉措。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://eurovisionworld.com/esc/the-favorit-to-win-eurovision-2020-we-should-be-allowed-to-perform-our-songs-in-2021|title=The favourite to win Eurovision 2020: "We should be allowed to perform our songs in 2021"|author=Rasmus|date=18 March 2020|work=Eurovisionworld |access-date=20 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320102431/https://eurovisionworld.com/esc/the-favorit-to-win-eurovision-2020-we-should-be-allowed-to-perform-our-songs-in-2021|archive-date=20 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> 然而，在2020年3月20日，參考小組决定，根據歐洲歌唱大賽的規則，2020年的歌曲將沒有資格參加2021年的比賽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/story/intention-to-honour-eurovision-2020-songs-artists|title=Intention to honour Eurovision 2020 songs and artists|date=20 March 2020|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|access-date=20 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320195055/https://eurovision.tv/story/intention-to-honour-eurovision-2020-songs-artists|archive-date=20 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>

