roadcasting Union|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514100803/https://eurovision.tv/live-blog-thursday-13-may/snippet/breaking-news-ukraines-kateryna-able-to-perform|archive-date=14 May 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

