=== COVID-19感染 ===
[[File:ESC2021_Rotterdam_Test_Pavilion.jpg|thumb]]
在“Turquoise Carpet”活動之前，波蘭和冰島代表團各有一名成員的COVID-19檢測為陽性。結果，這些代表團缺席了比賽，根據比賽的健康和安全規程進行了自我隔離。<ref>{{Cite web|date=15 May 2021|title=EBU Statement: Member of Polish Delegation tests positive for COVID-19|url=https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-member-of-polish-delegation-tests-positive-for-covid-19|access-date=16 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121195608/https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-member-of-polish-delegation-tests-positive-for-covid-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=16 May 2021|title=EBU Statement: Member of Icelandic Delegation tests positive for COVID-19|url=https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-member-of-icelandic-delegation-tests-positive-for-covid-19|access-date=16 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516223606/https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-member-of-icelandic-delegation-tests-positive-for-covid-19|dead-url=no}}</ref> 羅馬尼亞和馬耳他代表團也出於預防措施缺席了此次活動，因為他們與波蘭和冰島代表團住在同一家酒店。<ref>{{Cite web|date=16 May 2021|title=Further EBU Statement regarding participants of Turquoise Carpet Event (Sunday 16 May, 2021)|url=https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/further-ebu-statement-regarding-participants-of-turquoise-carpet-event-sunday-16-may-2021|access-date=16 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516193649/https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/further-ebu-statement-regarding-participants-of-turquoise-carpet-event-sunday-16-may-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>

波蘭和冰島代表團的所有其他成員的檢測結果均為陰性，並一直處於隔離狀態，直到參加第二場半決賽評委表演。<ref>{{Cite web|date=17 May 2021|title=Eurovision'21: Malta & Romania Released From Quarantine, Iceland & Poland Remain in Quarantine|url=https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/eurovision21-🇲🇹-malta-🇷🇴-romania-released-from-quarantine-🇮🇸-iceland-🇵🇱-poland-remain-in-quarantine/|url-status=no|access-date=18 May 2021|website=Eurovoix|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210729200035/https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/eurovision21-%F0%9F%87%B2%F0%9F%87%B9-malta-%F0%9F%87%B7%F0%9F%87%B4-romania-released-from-quarantine-%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B8-iceland-%F0%9F%87%B5%F0%9F%87%B1-poland-remain-in-quarantine/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Granger|first=Anthony|date=17 May 2021|title=Iceland: Daði og Gagnamagnið PCR Test Negative, Aiming to Return to Rehearsals on Wednesday|url=https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/iceland-dadi-og-gagnamagnid-pcr-test-negative/|url-status=no|access-date=18 May 2021|website=Eurovoix|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211007013254/https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/iceland-dadi-og-gagnamagnid-pcr-test-negative/}}</ref> 然而，後來證實，冰島代表{{tsl|en|Daði Freyr|多瑞·弗萊爾}}的一名成員的檢測結果為陽性，因此該隊退出了現場表演。在第二場半決賽的評委表演和現場表演中，他們在阿侯伊的彩排片段都被播放了；這段錄影也在決賽中播出。<ref name="Iceland COVID 1" /><ref name="Iceland COVID 2" /> 波蘭代表團的其餘成員隨後被解除隔離。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Granger|first=Anthony|date=19 May 2021|title=Poland: Rafał & Delegation Released From COVID-19 Isolation|url=https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/19/rafal-released-from-covid-19-isolation/|url-status=no|access-date=19 May 2021|website=Eurovoix|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210729200035/https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/19/rafal-released-from-covid-19-isolation/}}</ref>

5月20日，歐廣聯盟確認[[鄧肯·勞倫斯|鄧肯·勞倫斯]]檢測呈陽性，不會在決賽中現場表演。<ref>{{Cite web|date=20 May 2021|title=EBU Statement: Duncan Laurence tests positive for COVID-19|url=https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-duncan-laurence-tests-positive-for-covid-19|access-date=20 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|language=en-gb|archive-date=2021-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124092244/https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-duncan-laurence-tests-positive-for-covid-19|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他將在中場休息時表演他的獲獎歌曲〈[[電子遊樂場_(歌曲)|電子遊樂場]]〉和他的新單曲〈{{link-en|Stars (鄧肯·勞倫斯歌曲)|Stars (Duncan Laurence song)|Stars}}〉，並代表荷蘭評委陳述分數；後一個角色由{{link-en|羅米·蒙泰羅|Romy Monteiro}}代替，在決賽中播放了勞倫斯幕間式表演的預錄排練片段。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Romy Monteiro vervangt Duncan Laurence met puntentelling Eurovisie Songfestival {{!}} Eurovisie Songfestival|url=https://songfestival.nl/nieuws/romy-monteiro-vervangt-duncan-laurence-met-puntentelling-eurovisie-songfestival|access-date=22 May 2021|website=songfestival.nl|language=nl|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520144451/https://songfestival.nl/nieuws/romy-monteiro-vervangt-duncan-laurence-met-puntentelling-eurovisie-songfestival/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 由於檢測結果呈陽性，勞倫斯也沒有到場將獎盃移交給獲勝者；主持人將獎盃交給了現場觀眾。

決賽次日，挪威代表團一名成員檢測呈陽性，被迫留在鹿特丹接受隔離。後來證實，該代表團的另外六名成員在返回挪威後檢測呈陽性。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|title=Stort koronautbrudd i TIX sitt reisefølge - to er fortsatt i Rotterdam|url=https://www.tv2.no/a/14037267/|url-status=no|access-date=2021-06-03|website=TV 2|language=no|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109005533/https://www.tv2.no/a/14037267/}}</ref>

=== 技術問題 ===
==== 評委表演問題 ====
在第一場半決賽的評委表演中，羅馬尼亞、烏克蘭和馬耳他代表團報告了他們的表現問題；最值得注意的是，{{tsl|en|Roxen (singer)|羅克森}}在他們的歌曲〈失憶症〉"Amnesia" 的合唱中被認為是另類的。歐廣聯盟後來證實發生了[[入耳式耳機|入耳式耳機]]問題，所有涉及的參賽者都將獲得第二次表演機會。<ref>{{Cite web|date=17 May 2021|title=Eurovision'21: EBU Confirms In-Ear Issues For Malta, Romania & Ukraine|url=https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/eurovision21-ebu-confirms-in-ear-issues-malta-romania-ukraine/|url-status=no|access-date=25 May 2021|website=Eurovoix|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517205348/https://eurovoix.com/2021/05/17/eurovision21-ebu-confirms-in-ear-issues-malta-romania-ukraine/}}</ref> 在第二次演出沒有出現任何問題。

在[[聖馬利諾在欧洲歌唱大赛之歷年表現|聖馬利諾]]評委的最後一場表演中，旋轉平台沒有按預期停止，導致{{tsl|en|Senhit (singer)|森希特}}在跳舞時不得不從平台上跳下來。聖馬利諾代表團後來提出投訴，還聲稱由於這些時間問題，所有攝像鏡頭都失真了。代表團提出允許森希特和[[佛羅·里達|佛羅·里達]]退出活動，但他們最終決定留下。比賽的執行主管{{link-en|馬丁·厄斯特達爾|Martin Österdahl}}向代表團道歉，並重申這個問題將得到解決，他們將得到最高程度的保護。<ref>{{Cite web|date=22 May 2021|title=San Marino files formal protest after rotating platform "endangers" Senhit during Eurovision jury rehearsal|url=https://wiwibloggs.com/2021/05/22/san-marino-files-formal-protest-after-rotating-platform-endangers-senhit-during-eurovision-jury-show/265440/|access-date=23 May 2021|website=wiwibloggs|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523052839/https://wiwibloggs.com/2021/05/22/san-marino-files-formal-protest-after-rotating-platform-endangers-senhit-during-eurovision-jury-show/265440/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

