=== 對吸毒的虛假指控 ===
在決賽的歌手休息室部分，意大利樂隊[[天際月光樂團|天際月光樂團]]的主唱{{link-en|達米亞諾·大衛|Damiano David}}（Damiano David）被社交媒體上的一些在線觀眾聲稱，有人看到他俯身在桌子上吸了一口可卡因，儘管裡面沒有毒品。鏡頭和歌手坐在遠離桌子的地方，靠近意大利代表團成員。<ref>{{Cite web|date=23 May 2021|title=Eurovision 2021: Italian winners Maneskin deny doing drugs during ceremony|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/eurovision-italy-drugs-maneskin-cocaine-b1852349.html|author=Louis Chilton|access-date=23 May 2021|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523173353/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/eurovision-italy-drugs-maneskin-cocaine-b1852349.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=23 May 2021|title=Eurovision organisers say Maneskin singer will take voluntary drug test following cocaine use denial|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/eurovision-italy-drugs-maneskin-ebu-b1852409.html|author=Louis Chilton|access-date=23 May 2021|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123144448/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/eurovision-italy-drugs-maneskin-ebu-b1852409.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=23 May 2021|title=Måneskin, Damiano accusato di aver sniffato cocaina in diretta tv. La replica: "Non ditelo, io non uso droghe. Siamo pronti a fare il test"|url=https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_23/maneskin-damiano-accusato-aver-sniffato-cocaina-diretta-tv-replica-non-ditelo-io-non-uso-doghe-siamo-pronti-fare-test-bc101470-bb8d-11eb-822f-b2d049d46202.shtml|author=Chiara Maffioletti|access-date=24 May 2021|website=[[Corriere_della_Sera|Corriere della Sera]]|language=it|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028032835/https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_23/maneskin-damiano-accusato-aver-sniffato-cocaina-diretta-tv-replica-non-ditelo-io-non-uso-doghe-siamo-pronti-fare-test-bc101470-bb8d-11eb-822f-b2d049d46202.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在樂隊獲勝後的新聞發布會上，在瑞典報紙《{{link-en|體育畫報 (瑞典)|Aftonbladet|體育畫報}}》工作的記者托比昂·埃克（Torbjörn Ek）詢問了這些指控，大衛否認了這些指控，他暗示其他成員湯瑪斯·拉吉（Thomas Raggi）打碎了大衛從地板上撿起的玻璃杯，繼續說“我不吸毒，拜託大家，不要這麼說。”<ref>{{Cite news|last=Erdbrink|first=Thomas|date=22 May 2021|title=Eurovision Grand Final: Italy Takes Top Prize|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/05/22/world/eurovision-finals|access-date=23 May 2021|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106160209/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/05/22/world/eurovision-finals|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Ek|first=Torbjörn|date=23 May 2021|title=Eurovision-vinnarens svar till Aftonbladet efter tv-klippet: "Tar inte droger"|url=https://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/melodifestivalen/a/pA3dxW/eurovision-vinnarens-svar-till-aftonbladet-efter-tv-klippet-tar-inte|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523021911/https://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/melodifestivalen/a/pA3dxW/eurovision-vinnarens-svar-till-aftonbladet-efter-tv-klippet-tar-inte|archive-date=26 May 2021|work=Aftonbladet|language=sv}}</ref> 樂隊後來在他們的官方 [[Instagram|Instagram]] 帳戶上發表聲明說：“ 我們對某些人關於達米亞諾吸毒的言論感到非常震驚。我們真的反對毒品，我們從未使用過可卡因。我們已準備好接受測試，因為我們沒有什麼可隱瞞的。”<ref>{{Cite news|date=23 May 2021|title=What they're talking about at Eurovision in Rotterdam|language=en-US|work=[[France_24|France 24]]|publisher=[[France_Médias_Monde|France Médias Monde]]|url=https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20210523-what-they-re-talking-about-at-eurovision-in-rotterdam|access-date=23 May 2021|archive-date=2021-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211023043631/https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20210523-what-they-re-talking-about-at-eurovision-in-rotterdam|dead-url=no}}</ref> 歐廣聯盟第二天發表聲明，稱樂隊、他們的管理層和意大利代表團團長否認了任何指控，有關歌手也否認了這一指控。當天晚上，達米亞諾要求接受檢測，但由於無法立即組織檢測，他將“到家後自願進行藥物檢測”，並確認“現場檢查後發現玻璃碎”。<ref>{{Cite web|date=23 May 2021|title=EBU statement on Måneskin in the ESC Green Room during the Grand Final|url=https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-on-maneskin-in-the-esc-green-room-during-the-grand-final|access-date=23 May 2021|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|language=en-gb|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211132030/https://eurovision.tv/mediacentre/release/ebu-statement-on-maneskin-in-the-esc-green-room-during-the-grand-final|dead-url=no}}</ref> 指控案件大多被法國媒體強行報導，甚至得到法國外交部長[[让-伊夫·勒德里昂|让-伊夫·勒德里昂]]的評論，<ref>{{Cite magazine|date=23 May 2021|title=Maneskin Singer Agrees to Drug Test After Eurovision Cocaine Use Rumors|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/international/9576768/eurovision-winner-maneskin-drug-test|access-date=24 May 2021|magazine=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531021829/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/international/9576768/eurovision-winner-maneskin-drug-test/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但[[法國電視台|法國電視台]]宣布他們不會提出任何正式指控，而意大利媒體則對此進行了描述作為一個走得太遠並成為[[假新聞|假新聞]]的社交媒體笑話。<ref>{{Cite web|date=23 May 2021|title=I Maneskin sniffano coca". Le accuse dei francesi diventano un caso. Damiano: "Sciocchezze, farò il test|url=https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_23/eurovision-maneskin-sniffano-cocaina-francia-chiede-squalifica-8812f092-bbcf-11eb-822f-b2d049d46202.shtml|author=Stefano Montefiori|access-date=24 May 2021|website=[[Corriere_della_Sera|Corriere della Sera]]|language=it|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106160209/https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_23/eurovision-maneskin-sniffano-cocaina-francia-chiede-squalifica-8812f092-bbcf-11eb-822f-b2d049d46202.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=24 May 2021|title=I Måneskin all'Eurovision e la presunta droga, la tv francese prende le distanze dal ministro degli esteri: "Non faremo reclamo, vittoria meritata"|url=https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_24/maneskin-presunto-uso-coca-tv-stato-francese-prende-distanze-ministro-esteri-non-faremo-reclamo-vittoria-meritata-cfae3d8c-bc68-11eb-abb7-46b8b952d96c.shtml|author=Stefano Montefiori|access-date=24 May 2021|website=[[Corriere_della_Sera|Corriere della Sera]]|language=it|archive-date=2021-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009094024/https://www.corriere.it/spettacoli/21_maggio_24/maneskin-presunto-uso-coca-tv-stato-francese-prende-distanze-ministro-esteri-non-faremo-reclamo-vittoria-meritata-cfae3d8c-bc68-11eb-abb7-46b8b952d96c.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

